  {id: 254, name: "Robert Taylor", dob: "1963", bio: "Graduate of the prestigious West Australian Academy of Performing Arts (WAAPA).Many are unfamiliar with this Robert Taylor, but he has had an active career covering 20 years. Taylor has starred in many TV and film productions in Australia, the USA and on the BBC (Ballykissangel). Taylor is one of Australia's most respected film and television actors.", image_url: "http://ia.media-imdb.com/images/M/MV5BOTM1NTk5MzA4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTgwMTA5Nw@@._V1._SX214_CR0,0,214,314_.jpg"},
